high_descs: Turn left, move to the counter on the right, past the sink.
Pick up the potato on the counter.
Bring the potato to the fridge, on the left of that counter.
Chill the potato in the fridge.
Bring the chilled potato to the left sink, on your right.
Put the potato in the left sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled potato in the left sink.

high_descs: Go forward toward the door, then turn left and go to the counter ahead.
Pick up the potato on the counter.

Put the potato in the fridge and chill it, then take it out.
